0 0 6 Oct 13 18:42:28 2025                     
Rule File Pathname: _SMIC_CalDRC_40GELGLL_0911121825_2TM_V1.12.1_0.drc_
TV density under wire bond pad area checked with window size 10umx10um, step 5um. â¥ 10%
DRC check the (wire bond pad opening sd 1um) area.
DRC need check the TV within wire bond pad opening area , where density ratio= (TV area)/( wire bond pad opening area).
(1) Firstly exclude the region which is defined in the rule, then check the layer density.
(2) If design size is â¥ check window, please follow check window to check, if remained design size is < check window, please base on real size to check when the width of remained design â¥ (check window)/4 and <check window, and please ignore to check when the width of remained design < (check window)/4.
